reviewText: Good action flics, lots of eye candy, nice!!!
Good movies,great price. Delivered when promised.
Arrived on time and as advertised.
"Yeah Buddy!" Just what I wanted. I had never watched the complete movie,but this is a okay!
Cliffhanger was good for the vertical thrills of the mountains, good flick.  6th Day was descent with somewhat comedic moments during flick.rate it a 3. Haven't watched the other 2 movies yet.
I was looking for only one of the movies. Getting all four at the price of one was a great bonus.
I got this for Cliffhanger but who can't use a few extra 80-90's action movies!
